nodes.title: Workflow Information
widgets_values:
=== How to prompt this workflow ===

Main Prompt
-----------
The subject of the image in natural language

Example: a cat with a hat in a grass field


Secondary Prompt
----------------
A list of keywords derived from the main prompts, at the end references to artists

Example: cat, hat, grass field, style of [artist name] and [artist name]


Style and References Prompt
---------------------------
A description of the style of the image, the main style should be the first word and can be emphasized by surrounding it with ~*~

Example: ~*~painting~*~ oil painting, vibrant colors


Negative Prompt
---------------
Subjects that should not appear in the image

Example: jpeg artifacts, noise


Negative Style Prompt
---------------------
Styles and concepts that should not be used to generate the image

Example: photograph, anime
